<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <!-- Link to the CSS file for styling -->
    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/about.css"> --}}
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9; 
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff; 
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff; 
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff; 
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
        }


        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

 
        section {
            padding-bottom: 20px; 
        }

        section h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        section p {
            color: #333; 
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        
        section ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        section ul li {
            color: #333; 
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header section -->
        <header>
            <h1>About Better World Employment Services</h1>
        </header>

        <!-- Main content section -->
        <main>
            <!-- Mission section -->
            <section id="mission">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Empowering individuals by providing access to fulfilling employment opportunities that align with their skills, passions, and aspirations. We facilitate business growth by connecting them with talented professionals.</p>
            </section>

            <!-- Who We Are section -->
            <section id="who-we-are">
                <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                <p>A dedicated team bridging the gap between job seekers and employers. With our industry experience and passion for making a difference, we aim to revolutionize the job search process.</p>
            </section>

            <!-- What We Offer section -->
            <section id="what-we-offer">
                <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Comprehensive Job Listings</li>
                    <li>Tailored Recruitment Services</li>
                    <li>Career Resources and Guidance</li>
                    <li>Employer Branding Solutions</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Vision section -->
            <section id="vision">
                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                <p>Creating a better world through meaningful employment opportunities, where every individual thrives personally and professionally. By facilitating these connections, we aim to contribute to global growth and prosperity.</p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
